@Technoshaman777: There is an error in the url. To find the video it is going to look for your json_id and then the video_id which is the webtorrent. The json_id 163 doesn't have the video your are looking for. 

http://127.0.0.1:43110/1FUQPLXHimgCvYHH7v3bJXspJ7bMBUXcEb/?/watch/168/2fe737e407eada0e1ae8c1fe4c28cfd5c2fdaf02

This is the good url but there is no peer.

Once you got that you will need to update the value (OP_NAME_UPDATE) with the info of your site address like here https://namecha.in/name/d/mixtape (you don't need the `info` part only the `zeronet`. However the standard way is now : 
```
{
    "map": {
        "": { "zeronet":"19rXKeKptSdQ9qt7omwN82smehzTuuq6S9"}, 
        "staging": {"zeronet":"1MzSDy3x8cFrt3P2YkXNN7ogYDFfKX6hnP"}
    }
}
```

@Androiduser: Yes! Something like 
```
  {"zeronet":"19rXKeKptSdQ9qt7omwN82smehzTuuq6S9"}
